# ─── Stripe (test mode) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Create a Stripe account at https://stripe.com
# 2. Go to Developers → API keys → copy the test keys (sk_test_... / pk_test_...)
# 3. Create two recurring products (or use Stripe CLI):
#    stripe products create --name "Pro"
#    stripe prices create --product <pro_id> --unit-amount 900 --currency usd --recurring[interval]=month
#    stripe products create --name "Business"
#    stripe prices create --product <biz_id> --unit-amount 2900 --currency usd --recurring[interval]=month
# 4. Webhooks in dev: stripe listen --forward-to localhost:3000/api/stripe/webhook
#    Copy the webhook secret (whsec_...) printed by the CLI.
#    Events to enable: checkout.session.completed, customer.subscription.updated,
#                      customer.subscription.deleted, invoice.paid
